*HEADER GROWTH FACTOR 01-OCT-91 1EGF *COMPND EPIDERMAL GROWTH FACTOR (EGF) (NMR, 16 STRUCTURES) *SOURCE MOUSE (MUS MUSCULUS) *AUTHOR G.T.MONTELIONE,K.WUTHRICH,H.A.SCHERAGA *REVDAT 1 31-JAN-94 1EGF 0 REMARK 2 THE FOLLOWING THREE TABLES LIST ARE THE DISMAN INPUT FILES
REMARK 2 USED TO GENERATE THE SOLUTION STRUCTURES OF MURINE EGF REMARK 2 DESCRIBED IN THE JOURNAL ENTRY. Table I. Upper-bound Constraint List Murine Epidermal Growth Factor pH: 3.1, Temp: 28 deg
;

